description: Food provides essential nutrients for overall health and well-being
_details: Food is essential for human survival, providing the necessary nutrients, vitamins, and minerals that our bodies need to function properly. A balanced diet helps maintain energy levels, supports growth and development, and plays a key role in preventing chronic diseases
